description: FIGURE 1. Consensus of the two most parsimonious cladograms resulting from analyses of the matrix in Appendix 1. For characters and character states see Appendix 3. Asterisks: character changes supported by only one of the two most parsimonious cladograms. See Relationships section for further details.
name: FIGURE 1 in Revision and cladistic analysis of the Southeast Asian leaf-dwelling spider genus Calapnita Simon (Araneae, Pholcidae)
